    28→
    29→One COR24 emulator, one address space. The C compiler code and pvm.s coexist:
    30→
    31→```
    32→COR24 Memory:
    33→+---------------------------+
    34→| C compiler code (native)  |  tc24r output
    35→| pvm.s (VM interpreter)    |  linked together
    36→+---------------------------+
    37→| C globals, buffers        |
