    40→+---------------------------+
    41→| p-code bytecode (.p24)    |  runtime + user program
    42→+---------------------------+
    43→| VM eval stack             |
    44→| VM call stack             |
    45→| VM globals/heap           |
    46→+---------------------------+
    47→```
